desc: Try our Minnesota Locally grown produce! From fresh Gourmet Mushrooms, Microgreens, Foraged Mushrooms (including Morels!), and a variety of unique produce. We grow both Seasonal and year round mushrooms indoors and in a greenhouse. Greenhouse grown mushrooms are more bright in color and rich in vitamin D!

layout.text: Minnesota based urban farm cultivating mushrooms and unique produce with a focus on sustainability.
